---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure | SelectStream Shop">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 23, 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      <p>In compliance with the FTC guidelines, please assume that any and all links on this website are affiliate links. SelectStream Shop receives a small commission from sales of certain items, but the price is the same for you.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Amazon Associates Program</h2>
      <p>SelectStream is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com. As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Editorial Integrity</h2>
      <p>Our curations are based on aesthetic merit and technical excellence. We only feature products that align with the "Matte Black Standard" of minimalist workspace design. Commissions help support the autonomous curation engine and maintenance of the stream.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions regarding our affiliate relationships can be directed to: <span class="highlight">hello@selectstreamshop.com</span></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 8rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #999;
  }

  h1 { font-size: 3rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 3rem; letter-spacing: 0.1rem; }
  .last-updated { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #444; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .highlight { color: #fff; }
</style>
